League One Play-Off Semi Finalists: 2003/2004
League One Play-Off Finalists: 2004/2005
Trivia
Boyd considers himself as a big fan of former Arsenal player, Dennis Bergkamp. 23
During Hartlepool&lt;U+2019&gt;s pre-season tour in Holland, a streaker ran onto the pitch and danced in front of him. 24
As well as supporting Hartlepool, Boyd's other favourite team was Manchester United.25
